{
  "stem": "23090.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The adult may look-- may already know it in more-- in a more experienced because of being able to identify quicker.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I already started feeling that this was, like, a terrible place we're going.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- the-- because we now were seeing the abusiveness of the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were still treated a little more humane, because they didn't want to see that-- that last minute of possible-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I wouldn't call it a revolution, but certainly a-- some kind of a resistance.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they, to that point, they were still trying to whitewash it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But on the way to the wagons, it was just like-- like an inferno.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was just like people just-- w were herded.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And now the-- the-- the-- the beatings were going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The schnell, schnell, schnell, fast, fast, schnell, schnell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you can now see they were throwing people that couldn't walk fast enough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's prior to the camps now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm talking prior to the Auschwitz, where we were going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was no tolerance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was zero.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And now, my dad kept just saying, keep moving, keep moving, keep moving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they kept saying, just don't look back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Just keep moving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They didn't want me to get hit and my sister was starting to cry and there was crying and screaming and crying.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, hysteria was starting to become very, very clear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was seven years-- I was-- No, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was 10 and 1/2 at that point. 10 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was starting to be like a-- like a-- hys-- hysteria was everywhere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was everywhere, OK?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got to the train station, and it was like instantaneously.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
